22333407154</guid><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 17:02:33 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Earl K. Miller</title><link>https://fediscience.org/@ekmiller/111223409155050524</link><description>David Freedman with his first paper.  You never forget your first.Freedman, D.J., Riesenhuber, M., Poggio, T., and Miller, E.K. (2001) Categorical representation of visual stimuli in the primate prefrontal cortex. Science, 291:312-316.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://doi.org/10.1126/science.291.5502.312" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;doi.org/10.1126/science.291.55&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;02.312&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/111/223/409/259/072/105/original/4edc3c901aed4473.jpeg"&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/111/223/409/259/072/105/original/4edc3c901aed4473.jpeg" alt="Mastodon image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111223409303185725</guid><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 18:15:39 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Carl Zimmer</title><link>https://mastodon.social/@Carl_Zimmer/111223559443182663</link><description>Here is my story on a new brain atlas: 3300 cell types and counting… Gift link: &lt;a href="https://tinyurl.com/duzfw4df" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=""&gt;tinyurl.com/duzfw4df&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111223559443182663</guid><pubDate>Thu, 12 Oct 2023 18:53:52 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>nature :press:</title><link>https://press.coop/@Nature/111223422821198556</link><description>Reproducibility trial: 246 biologists get different results from same data setsNature, Published online: 12 October 2023; doi:10.1038/d41586-023-03177-1W