iginal/3864aba189bafcd6.jpg"&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/111/225/913/042/650/871/original/3864aba189bafcd6.jpg" alt="Mastodon image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111225913108849251</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 04:52:24 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Dorothy Bishop</title><link>https://mastodon.social/@deevybee/111226141080313819</link><description>A new report on the saga of &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mastodon.social/tags/Cassava" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Cassava&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; sciences development of &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mastodon.social/tags/simufilam" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;simufilam&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for  &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mastodon.social/tags/Alzheimers" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Alzheimers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Doctored images and missing data raise questions.&lt;br/&gt;why this investigation has been so slow?&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.science.org/content/article/co-developer-cassava-s-potential-alzheimer-s-drug-cited-egregious-misconduct" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://www.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;science.org/content/article/co&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;-developer-cassava-s-potential-alzheimer-s-drug-cited-egregious-misconduct&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mastodon.social/tags/fraud" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;fraud&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mastodon.social/tags/misconduct" rel="tag"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;misconduct&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111226731750043725</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 08:20:37 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>PCI RR</title><link>https://spore.social/@pcirr/111226463215086863</link><description>Following a breach of &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://spore.social/tags/RegisteredReport" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;RegisteredReport&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; evaluation norms, the Managing Board of &lt;span class="h-card" translate="no"&gt;&lt;a class="u-url mention" href="https://spore.social/@pcirr" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@&lt;span&gt;pcirr&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; has removed the Journal of Experimental Psychology: General from our list of PCI RR-interested journals &amp;amp; is launching an updated policy. &lt;br/&gt;Read our full statement: &lt;a href="https://osf.io/y23gm" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=""&gt;osf.io/y23gm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111226768193089094</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 08:29:53 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Gerard</title><link>https://mastodon.world/@gfarrell/111224341209572879</link><description>&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/111/224/341/233/709/667/original/2f300813bfe6c262.png"&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/111/224/341/233/709/667/original/2f300813bfe6c262.png" alt="Mastodon image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111227247870132448</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 10:31:53 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>PsychoPy</title><link>https://mastodon.social/@psychopy/111227837763889431</link><description>🌟 Come join us in Nottingham April 2024! 🌟 We will be hosting our 3 day in person workshop @notts_psych April 9th - 11th 2024. Come learn the ins and outs of PsychoPy and Pavlovia and get started making your next experiment!Details here 👉  &lt;a href="https://workshops.psychopy.org/3days/index.html#" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;workshops.psychopy.org/3days/i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;ndex.html#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111227837763889431</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 13:01:54 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Holly A. Gultiano</title><link>https://synapse.cafe/@axoaxonic/111225751003013389</link><description>Today people are talking about attractor dynamics in brains, making me remember this paper "Repeller Neural Networks" &lt;a href="https://doi.org/10.1103/PhysRevE.48.4091" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;doi.org/10.1103/PhysRevE.48.40&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;91&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and wondering if repellers (the opposite of attractors) can be applied to study decisions as well. Neurally activity falls into attractors of choices we make, so it might be driven away from repellers of unchosen options</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111228016003251257</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 13:47:12 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Daniel Nichanian</title><link>https://journa.host/@taniel/111227994744527565</link><description>Great news: after a long wait, &lt;span class="h-card" translate="no"&gt;&lt;a class="u-url mention" href="https://journa.host/@bolts" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@&lt;span&gt;bolts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; is finally on Apple News!If you use the app, please sign-up and you'll see our stories there! (Frankly, do so even if you use it yet: we need new places to find each other.)Here:&lt;a href="https://apple.news/T8bf2gexpTVKHtGXnJxFVcg" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;apple.news/T8bf2gexpTVKHtGXnJx&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;FVcg&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111228087158446099</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 14:05:19 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Manlio De Domenico</title><link>https://mathstodon.xyz/@manlius/111228747556895989</link><description>🚨Excited to announce the opening of 2 fully funded PhD and 3 senior research/postdoctoral 3y+ positions to work on the statistical physics of &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mathstodon.xyz/tags/ComplexNetworks" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;ComplexNetworks&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;!The focus will be on climate &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mathstodon.xyz/tags/resilience" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;resilience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; coupled complex processes.Join us: we'll have fun!&lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mathstodon.xyz/tags/ScienceJobs" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;ScienceJobs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://mathstodon.xyz/tags/Jobs" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Jobs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/111/228/747/778/204/535/original/763d5210cdc045ac.png"&gt;&lt;img src="https://files.mastodon.social/cache/media_attachments/files/111/228/747/778/204/535/original/763d5210cdc045ac.png" alt="Mastodon image" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111228748011491214</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 16:53:16 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>nature :press:</title><link>https://press.coop/@Nature/111228780574098108</link><description>ChatGPT use shows that the grant-application system is brokenNature, Published online: 13 October 2023; doi:10.1038/d41586-023-03238-5The fact that artificial intelligence can do much of the work makes a mockery of the process. It’s time to make it easier for scientists to ask for research funding. &lt;a class="mention hashtag" href="https://press.coop/tags/press" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;#&lt;span&gt;press&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-023-03238-5?utm_source=press.coop" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://www.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="ellipsis"&gt;nature.com/articles/d41586-023&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;-03238-5?utm_source=press.coop&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111229815040731799</guid><pubDate>Fri, 13 Oct 2023 21:24:45 +0000</pubDate></item><item><link>https://social.graves.cl/notes/9ktqet17xqv7vzj5</link><description>&lt;span&gt;I love this phrase from &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class="u-url mention" href="https://sigmoid.social/@garymarcus" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@garymarcus@sigmoid.social&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;“Blind fealty to the statistics of arbitrary data is not AGI. It’s a hack. And not one that we should want.”&lt;/span&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">111233982340618258</guid><pubDate>Sat, 14 Oct 2023 15:04:31 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Albert Cardona</title><link>https://mathstodon.xyz/@albertcardona/111234020218212045</link><description>&lt;span class="h-card" translate="no"&gt;&lt;a class="u-url mention" href="https://mastodon.social/@schoppik" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@&lt;span&gt;schoppik&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="h-card" translate="no"&gt;&lt;a class="u-url mention" href="https://mastodon.social/@celestelabedz" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;@&lt;span&gt;celestelabedz&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;The solar eclipse, streamed live from San Diego: &lt;a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SSdJ9jELHOU" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" translate="no"&gt;&lt;span class="invisible"&gt;https://www.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;s